    "scope": "Phase A — locked v1 vocabulary, extensible.",
    "rules": [
      "Adding a tag is a small PR: append + reviewer signoff.",
      "Removing or renaming a tag requires a migration that updates all downstream entries — rare, painful, document carefully.",
